OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Calleged 'extreme racism'
OL,6,FA number of police officers are under
OL,7,Finvestigation for alleged racial
OL,8,Fdiscrimination.
OL,10,FThe seven Greater Manchester Police
OL,11,F(GMP) officers are based at the Bury
OL,12,Fdivision, with the action stemming
OL,13,Ffrom "canteen banter" by experienced
OL,14,Fofficers both on and off duty.
OL,16,FA source said the allegations
OL,17,Fconcerned "extreme racism, calling
OL,18,Fpeople awful names and boasting about
OL,19,Fit in the station".
