OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Calleged 'extreme racism'
OL,6,FThe force said it had suspended five
OL,7,Fofficers and put two other on
OL,8,Frestricted duties following the
OL,9,Freport, with the police watchdog
OL,10,Fleading the investigation.
OL,12,FIn a statement, GMP said it was
OL,13,F"deeply concerned" by the allegations.
OL,15,F"We've suspended five officers and put
OL,16,Ftwo officers on restricted duties on
OL,17,Fthe Bury district following a report
OL,18,Fmade of racial discrimination," a
OL,19,Fspokesperson said.
