OL,6,F"GMP has a zero tolerance on
OL,7,Fdiscriminatory behaviour from any of
OL,8,Four officers and staff.
OL,10,F"We are deeply concerned by the
OL,11,Fallegations and will not hesitate to
OL,12,Ftake any action necessary.
OL,14,F"The Independent Office for Police
OL,15,FConduct (IOPC) are independently
OL,16,Finvestigating following our referral."
