OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Calleged 'extreme racism'
OL,6,FThe police watchdog said it had begun
OL,7,Fan investigation "following a referral
OL,8,Fregarding the conduct of Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police officers who are
OL,10,Falleged to have engaged in
OL,11,Fconversations of a discriminatory
OL,12,Fnature."
OL,14,FIt added: "We will investigate
OL,15,Fallegations that these officers openly
OL,16,Fengaged in conversations and either
OL,17,Fused, or failed to challenge,
OL,18,Foffensive language.
