OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Calleged 'extreme racism'
OL,6,F"We began an independent investigation
OL,7,Fon Thursday 4 July following a conduct
OL,8,Freferral from the force the day
OL,9,Fbefore. We are reviewing the available
OL,10,Fmaterial and will notify the officers
OL,11,Fof their status in our investigation."
OL,13,FIOPC Regional Director, Catherine
OL,14,FBates, said: "Officers are expected to
OL,15,Fmaintain exemplary standards of
OL,16,Fconduct and professionalism.
