OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Calleged 'extreme racism'
OL,6,F"This type of behaviour has the
OL,7,Fpotential to undermine the public's
OL,8,Fconfidence and trust in policing, in
OL,9,Faddition to the impact it has on
OL,10,Fofficers who conduct themselves with
OL,11,Fintegrity.
OL,13,F"We will conduct a thorough
OL,14,Finvestigation to establish the
OL,15,Fevidence and ensure any discriminatory
OL,16,Fbehaviour is dealt with appropriately.
